Rating: 3
Nice alternative to fat-laden fries! Crispy on the outside. Made as is and it was yummy. Made it in 9-inch non-stick oven-safe pan and used 3 large potatoes (sliced thinly with mandolin). Flipped it over with ease. Make sure potatoes are cooked! I kept on pressing down during baking every few minutes. Served it with sirloin steaks. One could easily add herbs/seasonings/various cheeses and jazz it up to their taste.

