Rating: 4
YUM! Potatoes Anna without the cream! I've always thought the cream ruined an otherwise perfect dish (I usually use chicken stock anyway!) But these were too too good. However, creature of overkill that I am, I used twice the number of potatoes peeled half of them), cooked it in a 12" cast iron pan, added about 20 minutes to the cooking time and had heaven! And not a crumb leftover!

